name: .89Z
summary: Learn about .89Z files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

instructions: You can use Texas Instruments TI Connect (Windows, Mac) to install the program an 89Z file contains on a TI-89 calculator. For detailed instructions, refer to your calculator's documentation.

If your 89Z file is packaged with 89Y files, be sure to send those files to your calculator along with the 89Z file. Some programs are split across 89Z and 89Y files; they will run correctly only if all their files are installed on a calculator.
